testSteps.description: Given I am at the LiveTraffic Website
When I click on the menu button
And I click "Traffic Cameras" button from the menu list

Then I should see list of Camera regions from All Cameras tab
| Camera_Region |
| Inner Sydney |
| Sydney North |
| Sydney West |
| Sydney South |
| Regional North |
| Regional South |
| All Regional |
| All NSW |
| All Sydney |
When I click "Sydney North" button from All Cameras List
Then I should Camera Region name "Sydney North" on page

Then I should see list of below cameras from "Sydney North" region
